contents.value:
```xml
<script><![CDATA[
  if (a < b && c > d) { doSomething(); }
]]></script>
```
**CDATA** sections are not parsed by the XML parser. Useful for code or text with `<`, `>`, `&`.

```xpath
/root/child            # direct child
//element              # anywhere in document
.//node[@attr]         # relative with attribute
//book[price>30]       # with predicate
text()                 # text content
//item[last()]         # last item
//item[position()<=3]  # first 3 items
```
**XPath** navigates and queries XML documents.
